<Layout title="Eliza's First Birthday">
	<main>
		<h1>Eliza's First Birthday</h1>
		<p>They grow up so fast! It seems like just last week that Eliza was born. Now she's turning one! We're so excited to celebrate with you. Please join us for a fun-filled day of food, games, friends, and family.</p>
		
		<h2>When?</h2>
		<p>
			<strong>Date: </strong>
			Saturday, October 7th, 2023
			<br/>
			<strong>Time: </strong>
			1:00pm - 4:00pm
		</p>
		
		<h2>Where?</h2>
		<address>
			Alstede Farms<br/>
			1 Alstede Farms Ln<br />
		  Chester, NJ 07930
		</address>
		<p style="margin-bottom: 1rem">
			<a href="https://www.alstedefarms.com/" target="_blank">
				Visit their Website
			</a>
		</p>
		<p>
			<a 
				href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Alstede+Farms/@40.779056,-74.713821,14z/data=!4m6!3m5!1s0x89c3990b3264ed17:0xd043541046a9664f!8m2!3d40.7789241!4d-74.7137164!16s%2Fg%2F1td7_0ft?hl=en-US&entry=ttu"
				target="_blank"
			>
				Get Directions
			</a>
		</p>
		
		<h2>What can we bring?</h2>
		<p>
			Please refrain from buying or giving presents. She's perfectly happy with what she has. However, if you're inclined, please consider contributing to <a href="https://accounts.franklintempleton.com/investor/college/-1lYU" target="_blank">Eliza's college fund</a>, or consider donating to <a href="/donate">one of these charities</a>.
		</p>

		<!-- todo: agenda -->

		<h2>Food</h2>
		The following food will be provided. Expect lunch around 1-2pm.
		
		<ul>
			<li>Penne Vodka</li>
			<li>Gluten Free Penne Vodka</li>
			<li>Sausage & Peppers (Gluten Free)</li>
			<li>Pizza</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>What else should we know?</h2>
		<ul>
			<li>The venue is outside, under a tent, so dress appropriately.</li>
			<li>Wear comfortable walking shoes, especially if you plan to come fruit picking.</li>
			<li>No alcohol is allowed on site.</li>
		</ul>
	</main>
</Layout>

